data.name: Label7.Text
data.value:
1. Click on SteamCMD logo and wait.
2. When the black window close itself, fill all textboxes and put your settings.
3. Open your ports. (7777 and 7778 recommended)
4. Allow ShooterGameServer.exe in your AV and allow ports traffic.
5. Click on "Turn On" and wait a moment.
6. Get IP address from the icon in notification area and add it to your favorite in Steam.
7. Launch game and enjoy.
